{"tid":307147,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[港豬惡夢]李嘉誠注資Nomadic推廣走動式VR","createTime":"2017-07-03T06:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T10:34:45.000Z","uid":70786,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71416048e1bb58ce2952f255d6437d401aab5edc","tid":307147,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T06:28:20.000Z","msg":"虛擬實境（VR）成為近年熱門話題，最簡單一個紙盒加電話即可看到360度的影片。長和系主席李嘉誠早前就私人投資了美國一間「走動式VR」公司Nomadic。雖然正式產品要明年第一季才推出，但李嘉誠已率先將Nomadic引入香港。Nomadic行政總裁Doug Griffin認為，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港的住屋環境細小，反而更有利「走動式VR」發展。</span><br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠旗下私人投資旗艦維港投資，早前領投Nomadic種子輪融資，金額近600萬美元（約4,680萬港元）。<span style=\"color: red;\">李嘉誠早前亦率先將Nomadic引入香港，於黃埔舉辦的「香港競XP」活動中讓市民免費試玩。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n到時誠哥起100呎以下單位<br />\n買樓送個VR背囊<br />\n用VR擴充虛擬實用面積<br />\n返屋企孭個背囊即可體驗幾百呎多房生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef9e29afe95b7d00d7a91e34d0b289f15cda341","tid":307147,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T06:33:37.000Z","msg":"奶波魔快D入嚟講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b747774a826f3bc2e94d3bcbc357752036d3df5","tid":307147,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T06:47:09.000Z","msg":"奶波魔居然唔入嚟屌柒吸血鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c46c37d2f68ae8b2f71f65f340cd25a164329d","tid":307147,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7940426cabc5c0c966efe839a7cf7033cde48f","tid":307147,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T13:23:50.000Z","msg":"5連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b080d7b67ee1300cd8269ea984aa18761e0ae7","tid":307147,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco